Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Freezer Areas: 100% freezer-capable, designed with (5) 52,640 SF freezer areas (flexible temperatures to accommodate cooler as needed)
Battery Charging: spec for (2) 1,680 SF areas
Clear Height: 50 clear in warehouse; 30 clear in cold dock
Loading: (50) dock high doors with vertical hydraulic levelers & (2) ramps
Truck Court: 205 truck court, with trailer storage opposite from loading

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
Immediate proximity to I-20 with access to (3) interstates in under 4 miles
	Strong industrial location to accommodate both local and regional distribution
	Established industrial corporate presence
	Neighbors include the newly-announced 1.9M SF Walmart complex, which includes 700K SF of refrigerated space, Amazon, FedEx, UNFI, QCD, Lindt, Olam, Niagara Waters, Constellation Brand, Smuckers, and others

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Class A, state-of-the-art freezer/cooler facility. 50 clear height, 60,000+ pallet positions
	Flexible for single-tenant or multi-tenant freezer or cooler requirements (52,640 SF  343,250 SF)
	Strong visibility and almost immediate interstate access
	Heavy parking with dual entrances for optimal flow
